  },
  "slug": "no-bake-lemon-cheesecake",
  "title": "No-bake lemon cheesecake",
  "subtitle": "Fridge-set cheesecake with a sharp lemon filling",
  "excerpt": "A fridge-set cheesecake with a digestive biscuit base and a cream cheese filling sharpened with fresh lemon. No gelatine, no oven. Holds its shape when sliced and cut.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "The no-bake cheesecake is a British domestic formula of the mid-twentieth century. The method (whipped double cream folded into cream cheese for stability without gelatine) is documented in British domestic cookery from the 1960s onwards. The lemon version is one of the two most common flavours alongside strawberry.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "No-bake lemon cheesecake is a fridge-set dessert with a crushed biscuit base and a sharp cream cheese filling. No oven, no gelatine. The filling sets in the fridge overnight and holds clean slices. It serves 10 to 12 from a 23 cm springform tin."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Two things make it work. The lemon must be fresh: bottled juice lacks the oils that give fresh lemon its brightness. And the cream must only reach "
          },
          {
            "text": "soft peaks",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpaeh8o8000018v48l0517ui"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " before folding in. Over-whipped cream makes the finished filling grainy."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "ingredientsGroup",
            "attrs": {
              "title": "Base"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "digestive-biscuits",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 250,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "unsalted-butter",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": "melted",
                  "quantity": 100,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "ingredientsGroup",
            "attrs": {
              "title": "Filling"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "full-fat-cream-cheese",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 600,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "icing-sugar",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": "sifted",
                  "quantity": 100,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "double-cream",
                  "unit": "ml",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 300,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "lemons",
                  "unit": null,
                  "prepNote": "zest and juice (about 60 ml juice)",
                  "quantity": 2,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Method"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Make the base"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Crush the {{digestive-biscuits}} to fine crumbs in a food processor or in a sealed bag with a rolling pin."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Mix with the melted {{unsalted-butter}} until the crumbs are evenly dampened. Press into the base of the springform tin in an even layer. Refrigerate while you make the filling."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Make the filling"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Beat the {{full-fat-cream-cheese}} and {{icing-sugar}} together until smooth. Stir in the zest and juice of the {{lemons}}."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "In a separate bowl, whip the {{double-cream}} to soft peaks. Fold the whipped cream into the cream cheese mixture in three additions."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Chill, 6 hours minimum"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Spoon the filling onto the biscuit base and smooth the top. Refrigerate for at least 6 hours, overnight if possible."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "To unmould, run a warm knife around the inside of the tin before unclipping. Serve straight away."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
